#X text 23 30 The [phaser~] object is an abstraction that implements a Phaser with [allpass.filt~]. It is still a rather low level unit where you have to implement and feed the frequency LFO from the outside. Below we have a triangular waveform for the LFO and the frequency sweep is pitch in MIDI \, then it's converted to frequency., f 61;
